data.description: Bring your horses and your toys to this picturesque 4.13-acre property, where the possibilities are as vast as the breathtaking mountain views. This 2170 sq ft home, is a perfect blend of modern elegance and rural charm. Step inside this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, and you'll be greeted by a bright eat-in kitchen with white cabinets, granite countertops, tile accents, farmhouse sink, stainless steel appliances and large island. French doors lead to your wrap-around porch. Complete remodel with modern finishes, granite counters and wood look floors throughout. The new roof and air conditioner ensure both comfort and efficiency. Master suite features a walk-in closet, dual vanities, and a spa like soaking tub. Step outside to your fenced in yard. The property includes so much more!
